I like you.

4
00:00:24,177 --> 00:00:27,977
If you were a cake, I would eat you every day.

5
00:00:33,177 --> 00:00:36,811
I happened to experience some good things.

6
00:00:37,477 --> 00:00:39,203
That sounds interesting.

7
00:00:39,203 --> 00:00:42,844
By the way, thanks for helping with the contract.

8
00:00:42,844 --> 00:00:46,879
Well, you worked hard to get that contract.

9
00:00:46,879 --> 00:00:48,044
I cheer for you.

10
00:00:48,044 --> 00:00:51,011
Then I'm going.

11
00:00:51,644 --> 00:00:53,611
Good luck.

12
00:00:54,411 --> 00:00:59,977
Oh no, I can't help but smile.

13
00:01:00,744 --> 00:01:02,477
Shioya-san.

14
00:01:03,944 --> 00:01:05,811
I like you.

15
00:01:05,811 --> 00:01:07,744
I like you, too.

16
00:01:08,411 --> 00:01:13,944
I might have liked you even before you liked me.

17
00:01:14,977 --> 00:01:18,644
Was it when I was still in the General Affairs Department?

18
00:01:18,644 --> 00:01:20,583
I recall after a department assignment,

19
00:01:20,583 --> 00:01:24,215
the first time Shioya-san talked to me was…

20
00:01:26,710 --> 00:01:28,444
Sato-san.

21
00:01:29,910 --> 00:01:31,377
Have you a moment?

22
00:01:31,377 --> 00:01:33,577
Really?

23
00:01:35,044 --> 00:01:37,177
At that time…

24
00:01:39,610 --> 00:01:41,543
Sato.

25
00:01:41,543 --> 00:01:43,067
Yes.

26
00:01:43,067 --> 00:01:45,144
Can you come here a moment?

27
00:01:45,710 --> 00:01:47,444
Okay.

28
00:01:54,677 --> 00:01:57,619
Are you free tonight?

29
00:01:59,644 --> 00:02:03,144
I am. Is there a meeting?

30
00:02:03,144 --> 00:02:06,731
No, I have something to tell you.

31
00:02:06,731 --> 00:02:08,810
You have something to tell me?

32
00:02:09,977 --> 00:02:11,210
Come to my place tonight.

33
00:02:11,210 --> 00:02:13,939
Wh-What?

