288
00:23:06,410 --> 00:23:09,991
Usuda and I are friends.

289
00:23:09,991 --> 00:23:12,810
I will always stand by you forever, Kaede.

290
00:23:12,810 --> 00:23:17,071
Shioya-san was the person who saved me.

